song_lyrics: Akaḷ kaḷā tārī kaḷī koṇ jāṇe,
Jeṇe jem jāṇyu te tem tāṇe... ° 1
Sur nar munivar pār na pāme,
Sheṣh Sahasra mukh lesh na lādhe... ° 3
Prem thakī pragaṭ, chhaḷ thakī chhāno...° 4
title: Akaḷ kaḷā tārī kaḷī koṇ jāṇe
